textbox_5.text:
-4 for contrasting colours e.g. purple and orange.
-1 or -2 for similar colours e.g. dark blue and light blue
textbox_7.text: On a very small number of trials I found it difficult to see the second colour when it flashed up. This was often when the first circle was pale blue. I assume the second colour may have been grey and blended with the screen.
